### Deeds — Log good deeds, list, stats, AI image generation

### Log a good deed
POST {{host}}/api/deeds
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "childId": "{{childId}}",
  "description": "Helped with dishes",
  "imageType": "emoji",
  "imageValue": "🍽️"
}

###

### List deeds for a specific child
GET {{host}}/api/deeds?childId={{childId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get weekly + total deed stats for all children
GET {{host}}/api/deeds/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Generate AI image for a deed description
POST {{host}}/api/deeds/generate-image
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "a child helping with dishes, cartoon style"
}
